    <style>
        blockstart header-top {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            padding-left: 7.0rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #eee;
            font-family: 'PT Sans', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
        }

        blockstart header-bottom {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding-left: 7.0rem;
            padding-right: 7.0rem;
            color: #eee;
            font-family: 'PT Sans', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        blockstart header-bottom > * {
            --margins: 0.2rem; 

            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding-top: 0.05rem;
            margin-bottom: var(--margins);
            margin-top: var(--margins);
        }

        blockstart header-bottom sub-title {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        blockstart search-box {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding-left: 7.0rem;
            padding-right: 7.0rem; 
        }

        blockstart search-box color-box {
            padding-top: 50px;
            padding-bottom: 100px;
            padding-left: 50px;
            padding-right: 50px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color:#4C5A65;
        }

        blockstart search-box input[type="text"] {
            width: 80%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        blockstart search-box input[type="submit"] {
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        blockstart search-box search-options {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            padding: 5px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #eee;
        }

        blockstart search-box > * {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 5px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #eee; 
        }

        blockstart search-box ul {
            list-style-type: none; 
        }

    </style>
    <blockstart>
        <header-top>
            <h1>Welcome to NYC Ticket Tracker</h1>
        </header-top>
        <header-bottom>
            <sub-title>Discover Your NYC Ticket History</sub-title>
            <p>Welcome to NYC Ticket Tracker, your one-stop solution for managing your parking fines and traffic violations in New York City. With our user-friendly platform, you can easily look up your license plate and gain insight into your ticket history by year.</p>
            <p>Stay in control of your expenses and avoid surprises by tracking your ticket costs effortlessly. Start saving money and managing your NYC tickets today with NYC Ticket Tracker!</p>
        </header-bottom>
